## Creating a new Ticket

<%= partial "includes/requests/post", locals: {
      url: "https://api.tito.io/v2/an-account/awesome-conf/tickets",
      parameters: {
        data: {
          type: "tickets",
          attributes: {
            email: 'joe.bloggs@example.com'
          },
          relationships: {
            release: {
